<view class="page-bepartner">
  <image class="banner" src="/assets/images/apply_banner.jpg" mode="aspectFit" />
  <view wx:if="{{condition && condition.length}}" class="condition-box">
    <view class="condition-header">申请条件</view>
    <view class="line-separator-h"></view>
    <view class="condition-content">
      <view wx:for="{{condition}}" wx:key="title" class="condition-item">
        <text class="condition-text">{{index + 1}}.{{item.text}}</text>
        <text class="condition-icon lutufont{{item.value ? ' lutu-duihao' : ' lutu-chahao'}}"></text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="statement-wrapper">
    <view class="statement-box">
      <view class="statement-header theme-color">怎样“推广赚钱”</view>
      <view class="statement-content">分享平台内的推广商品，吸引好友点击，在一定时间内，TA在平台上购买任何推广商品，您都可以获得与订单金额成一定比例的收益。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="statement-box">
      <view class="statement-header theme-color">合伙人等级概况</view>
      <view class="statement-content">1. 合伙人等级分为初级、中级、高级</view>
      <view class="statement-content">① 用户通过合伙人审核，将自动成为初级合伙人</view>
      <view class="statement-content">② 成为中级合伙人和高级合伙人有相应的门槛要求</view>
      <view class="statement-content">2. 当合伙人达到相应要求时，系统将自动实现等级变更。</view>
      <view class="statement-content">3. 等级越高的合伙人将获得更高的收益。</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<ft-bottom-box wx:if="{{loaded}}" box-height="{{142}}">
  <view class="apply-btn-wrapper" hover-class="none" hover-stop-propagation="false">
    <button class="apply-btn{{(can_apply && fenxiao_user_status == 2 && !submitting) ? ' theme-linear-gradient-137' : ' disabled'}}" disabled="{{fenxiao_user_status === 0 || fenxiao_user_status === '0' || submitting}}" catchtap="showApplyModal">
      <text class='apply-text'>{{btnText[fenxiao_user_status] || '立即申请'}}</text>
    </button>
  </view>
</ft-bottom-box>
<ft-modal id="c-ft-modal" hide-cancel mode="2">
  <view slot="top" class="apply-modal">
    <view class="apply-box" catchtap="stopPropagation">
      <view class="apply-box-title">合伙人信息</view>
      <view class="card">
        <view class="line-separator-h"></view>
        <view class='item row ai-center jc-between'>
          <text class='title'>头像</text>
          <image class='avatar' src="{{user.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        </view>
        <view class='line-separator-h'></view>
        <view class='item row ai-center jc-between'>
          <text class='title'>昵称</text>
          <text class='value'>{{user.nick_name}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class='line-separator-h'></view>
        <view class='item row ai-center jc-between'>
          <text class='title'>手机号</text>
          <text class='value' wx:if="{{user.phone}}">{{user.phone}}</text>
          <button class='getPhone' hover-class="none" wx:if="{{!user.phone}}" open-type="getPhoneNumber" bindgetphonenumber='getPhoneNumber'>
            <text class='input-placeholder'>绑定手机</text>
            <text class='lutufont lutu-next2'></text>
          </button>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="line-separator-h"></view>
      <form report-submit bindsubmit="apply">
        <button form-type="submit" class="confirm-btn{{(user.phone && !submitting) ? ' theme-linear-gradient-137' : ' disabled'}}" disabled="{{!user.phone || submitting}}">
          <text class='confirm-text'>确定</text>
        </button>
      </form>
    </view>
  </view>
</ft-modal>
  